CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Men and women, including Alma Illery, David L. Lawrence, Cardinal John Wright, Frankie Mae Pace, and Monsignor Paul Bassompierre, in front, with Lois Dorsay, Mary Lane, and possibly Barbara Goggins, in back, seated in Central Baptist Church hall interior with certificate for Ladies' Auxiliary of the Knights of St John on wall
